{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-mateo/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-meet-mateo","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U španskom jeziku, pozdravi kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenos días</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches</span> prate pravila rodskog slaganja između prideva i imenica:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Días</span> (\"masiku\") je maskulinumska imenica, stoga pridev je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenos</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tardes</span> (\"mchana\") i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">noches</span> (\"usiku\") je ženski rod imenica, stoga pridjev je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas</span>.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Vreme dana</th>\n<th>Pozdrav</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Jutro</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenos días</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Podne</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Noć</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Fraza <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes</span> se koristi za pozdravljanje osobe od podne do zalaska sunca.</p>\n<p>Doslovno, to znači \"dobar dan\" ili \"dobro veče\", u zavisnosti od doba dana.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i odgovor na pitanje koje je navedeno ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-mateo/task-1"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Kakvu pozdravu koristi Mateo?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenos días.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova pozdrava se koristi ujutro, a ne popodne.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovaj pozdrav se obično koristi noću ili pred spavanje.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¡Buenas!</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovaj neformalan pozdrav može se koristiti u bilo kojem trenutku, ali ne znači nužno \"dobar dan\".</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Mateo","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_meet_mateo.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0.45,"finishTimestamp":2.11},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.66,"dialogue":{"text":"Hola, buenas tardes.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.16,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Uočenje 1","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-meet-mateo","dashedName":"task-1","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-introducing-yourself","block":"es-a1-learn-meet-mateo","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn